Hi and thanks for checking out my Turo profile, my name is Isaiah and I'm a local Business Owner & major car enthusiast!🚗

I've always loved trying out new cars when going on travel but lately it seems as though companies like Hertz & Enterprise have had little to no inventory, so I decided to do a bit of research and stumbled upon Turo.  It's been a great platform to use, which made me want to try it out for myself with my own personal car... fast forward to today and now there is a growing thriving Turo community in the Hampton Roads area!👍🏽

Feel free to check out the vehicles available, and l hope you'll check-in occasionally and see what new vehicles have been added recently.  I'll also post updates on stories, so if you're interested in seeing what new vehicles might be in the works, join me on Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/sova_ig/?hl=en

Thanks again!😁

My wife and I are doing a team project called Turo. My background is in maintaining industrial machines for international companies. Some of my favorite things are following the news, hobby stock analyzing, and maintaining a great fitness regiment. My wife, on the other hand, is an educator. Her place of enjoyment usually includes serving those that have issues advocating for themselves/ getting basic needs met or some form of writing. Whether its legal writing, a children’s book, or currently, trying her hand at script writing, writing is definitely fun for her. When she wanted us to write a script together, it felt more like work for me. 

In her early years out of college she was a manager at Hertz Rental cars, and I just love nice cars/business; so this is project that is fun for both of us!

Hi, I'm Reinah! Local entrepreneur, fitness enthusiasts and foodie.  I'm best described as a bubbly intorvert. I love being a mentor and friend to all.  I enjoy growing and leading with kindness and understanding.   I'm kinda a jack of all trades, which is probably why I'm drawn to hosting on Turo.

Meet a friendly car enthusiast who spent 20 years mastering the art of graphics. Now, I'm excited to share my love for cars by offering them to others. Let's create unforgettable experiences together!

"My happiness stems from the little things, like knowing my car has made a positive impact in someone's journey. It's the satisfaction of knowing that I've played a part in helping others that brings me immense joy."

Hi there! Thank you for considering one of our vehicles. Between each and every guest our cars are cleaned, washed, and sanitized for your safety. We have a wide variety to choose from, SUVs  to economy cars. Guest with 4.0 or below ratings will receive an automatic trip cancellation with our vehicles. This is to ensure 5 star guests will receive the highest quality vehicles and experience we can provide. There is no smoking or pets permitted in any of our vehicles and any indication of such will result in fines. Thanks again for considering us!
